sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Prospect
    participant Portal as /chat Portal
    participant API as /api/chat
    participant Regex as Regex Engine
    participant Groq as Groq (Llama)
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant Broker as Broker Dashboard

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 1 — Session Start
    U->>Portal: Opens /chat (logged in via Supabase Auth)
    Portal->>Portal: Load existing sessions for this email
    Portal->>U: Show sessions sidebar + "New session" button
    U->>Portal: Clicks "New inquiry" (or "Follow-up on existing")
    Portal->>API: POST {message, sessionType, parentLeadId?}
    API->>DB: INSERT lead (status: chatting, ticket_number via sequence)
    API-->>Portal: {leadId, reply: "Hi [Name]! I'm Aria..."}
    Portal-->>U: Welcome message + structured inputs

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 2 — Conversational Capture
    U->>Portal: Selects occupation from CHOICES pill
    Portal->>API: POST {message: "Salaried – Government / PSU"}
    API->>Regex: extractFieldsFromMessage()
    Regex-->>API: {occupation: "Salaried – Government / PSU"}
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {occupation} immediately
    API->>Groq: full conversation history
    Groq-->>API: reply + LEAD_DATA:{...} (if AI emits it)
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead from LEAD_DATA fields
    API->>DB: syncProfileToSiblings() — propagate to all leads with same email

    U->>Portal: NUMBER_INPUT widget → enters age "35"
    Portal->>API: POST {message: "I am 35 years old"}
    API->>Regex: extractFieldsFromMessage()
    Regex-->>API: {age: 35}
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {age: 35} immediately

    U->>Portal: Selects income from CHOICES pill
    Portal->>API: POST {message: "₹12–20 lakhs"}
    API->>Regex: extractFieldsFromMessage()
    Regex-->>API: {annual_income: 1600000}
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {annual_income} immediately

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 3 — Qualification
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {status: qualified, score: X}
    DB->>Broker: Realtime postgres_changes UPDATE → dashboard live-updates
    Broker->>Broker: LeadCard shows #0003 ticket + score

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 4 — Document Upload
    U->>Portal: Uploads existing policy PDF
    Portal->>API: POST /api/documents {file, leadId}
    API->>DB: INSERT document (status: processing)
    API->>API: pdf-parse extracts text layer
    API->>Groq: extraction prompt (Claude fallback if needed)
    Groq-->>API: {policy_type, sum_insured, exclusions, renewal_date, ...}
    API->>DB: INSERT extracted_data
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {status: processing}
    DB->>Broker: Realtime push → properties panel refreshes live

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 5 — Analysis Generation
    Broker->>API: POST /api/analysis {leadId}
    API->>DB: fetch lead profile + all extracted_data + conversation
    API->>Groq: Arjun Kapoor consultant persona + full client context
    Groq-->>API: {coverage_gaps, risk_flags, recommendation, priority, confidence_score}
    API->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE analyses
    API->>DB: UPDATE lead {status: completed}

    Note over U,Broker: Phase 6 — Follow-up Session (optional)
    U->>Portal: Clicks "Question about existing" in new session modal
    U->>Portal: Selects parent session from picker
    Portal->>API: POST {sessionType: follow_up, parentLeadId: X}
    API->>DB: INSERT lead {parent_lead_id: X, session_type: follow_up}
    API-->>Portal: "Hi [Name]! I can see this is a follow-up on your health enquiry..."
    DB->>Broker: New follow-up ticket appears on board with amber "Follow-up" badge
